titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: OTHER SURGICAL ACCESS TYPE (HEAD AND NECK CANCER) - Description

div.p: OTHER SURGICAL ACCESS TYPE (HEAD AND NECK CANCER) is the same as attribute CLINICAL INTERVENTION TEXT STRING.
OTHER SURGICAL ACCESS TYPE (HEAD AND NECK CANCER) is free text to specify the surgical access type, where SURGICAL ACCESS TYPE FOR HEAD AND NECK CANCER is National Code 'Other (not listed)'.
